---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Worship — Weekly Prayer Plan"
  description="A full weekly prayer plan that rotates through seven distinct postures — Ask, Study, Intercede, Bless, Repent, Praise, and Meditate — each with a descriptive guide and reflection questions."
>
  <div class="takeaways-content pp-page">
    <span class="takeaways-tag">Worship</span>
    <h1 class="takeaways-title">Weekly Prayer Plan</h1>
    <p class="pp-subtitle">Seven postures. One complete prayer life.</p>

    <div class="pp-grid">

      <!-- MONDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-monday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Monday</h2>
          <p class="pp-descriptors">Personal · Surrendered · Expectant</p>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Ask</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-body">
          <p class="pp-guide">Set aside time for quiet, focused prayer, seeking God's direct intervention in your life. Begin by surrendering distractions and opening your heart to the Holy Spirit's leading. Present your personal needs, desires, and concerns to God with open hands, trusting in His provision and protection. Seek wisdom and discernment for decisions, and pray for genuine heart transformation. Conclude by listening for His gentle promptings and jotting down any insights.</p>
          <div class="pp-reflect-section">
            <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
            <ul class="pp-reflect-list">
              <li>What's one area where I'm longing for God to move in my own life?</li>
              <li>Where do I need God's wisdom and discernment in my current circumstances?</li>
              <li>What area of my heart do I need God to transform?</li>
              <li>Lord, what do You want me to take away from this time?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- TUESDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-tuesday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Tuesday</h2>
          <p class="pp-descriptors">Attentive · Curious · Receptive</p>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Study</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-body">
          <p class="pp-guide">Read one scripture passage slowly, jotting down questions, key words, commands, etc. Use commentary to understand the historical background, cultural context, and deeper meaning of the passage. Identify key themes and truths, then select a verse to commit to memory. Allow these words to resonate throughout your day, shaping your thoughts and perspectives. Reflect on the passage, and invite God to embed its message within your heart and guide you in its application.</p>
          <div class="pp-reflect-section">
            <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
            <ul class="pp-reflect-list">
              <li>What is the author trying to communicate?</li>
              <li>What questions do I have that commentary might help with?</li>
              <li>Which specific verse will I practice reciting throughout my day?</li>
              <li>How can the key message shape my thoughts, decisions, or attitudes this week?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- WEDNESDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-wednesday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Wednesday</h2>
          <p class="pp-descriptors">Compassionate · Expanding · Faithful</p>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Intercede</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-body">
          <p class="pp-guide">Expand your prayer focus today to intercede for others, encompassing your personal circle, your community, and the wider world. Lift up specific individuals, including leaders, missionaries, and those facing persecution. Pray scriptural promises over these groups, asking God to move powerfully in their lives and circumstances. If you feel compelled, send a text to check in on their prayer requests, and let them know you prayed.</p>
          <div class="pp-reflect-section">
            <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
            <ul class="pp-reflect-list">
              <li>Who is facing a spiritual battle or needs breakthrough?</li>
              <li>Who is experiencing relational pain or needs healing?</li>
              <li>Who needs provision, protection, or guidance through a crisis?</li>
              <li>Name one area in the world where I'm longing for God to move.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- THURSDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-thursday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Thursday</h2>
          <p class="pp-descriptors">Generous · Servant-hearted · Active</p>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Bless</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-body">
          <p class="pp-guide">Focus today on actively extending God's grace and love to others. Think of several acts of service, thoughtful gifts, or words of affirmation that you could offer that reflect Christ's servant heart. Then ask the Holy Spirit for courage to initiate, humility to serve quietly, and wisdom to bless in ways that are actually helpful. Let your prayers fuel these actions, and allow these actions to deepen your prayer life, reinforcing your commitment to living out your faith.</p>
          <div class="pp-reflect-section">
            <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
            <ul class="pp-reflect-list">
              <li>How can I help carry someone else's burden and walk alongside them today?</li>
              <li>How can I better reflect God's unconditional love to those who are difficult to love?</li>
              <li>Who needs what I have (time, money, knowledge, influence, skills) right now?</li>
              <li>If Jesus physically walked into my day today, where would He go, and who would He stop for?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- FRIDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-friday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Friday</h2>
          <p class="pp-descriptors">Humble · Honest · Transforming</p>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Repent</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-body">
          <p class="pp-guide">Approach God with humility today, acknowledging and confessing areas where you have fallen short. Kneel or bow in prayer, honestly naming pride, selfishness, or any other sin that has hindered your relationship with Him or others. Ask for both forgiveness and transformation, trusting in His boundless mercy. Commit to a specific, tangible change this week, relying on His power to renew your heart and guide you toward an opposite act of obedience.</p>
          <div class="pp-reflect-section">
            <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
            <ul class="pp-reflect-list">
              <li>Where have I relied on my own wisdom instead of trusting God's lead?</li>
              <li>How has my pride, selfishness, or judgment wounded someone I was meant to love?</li>
              <li>When did I opt for comfort or distraction over wholehearted devotion?</li>
              <li>Is there a conversation, confession, or confrontation I'm avoiding?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- SATURDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-saturday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Saturday</h2>
          <p class="pp-descriptors">Grateful · Reflective · Worshipful</p>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Praise</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-body">
          <p class="pp-guide">Think back on your week and choose three moments: one highlight, one struggle, and one ordinary instance. For each, consider how God was at work — whether protecting, providing, teaching, or refining you. Then make two lists side by side: on the left, write specific things you're thankful for ("Thank You for..."); on the right, write what each blessing shows you about who God is ("I praise You because You are..."). End by thanking Him for being present in both the peaks and the valleys.</p>
          <div class="pp-reflect-section">
            <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
            <ul class="pp-reflect-list">
              <li>What blessing from this week am I most grateful for?</li>
              <li>In what ways has God met my needs or answered my prayers recently?</li>
              <li>What's one complaint from this week I can let go of and replace with a thankful heart?</li>
              <li>Which attribute or name of God am I most drawn to as I reflect on the week?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- SUNDAY -->
      <article class="pp-card" id="day-sunday">
        <div class="pp-card-top">
          <h2 class="pp-day">Sunday</h2>
          <p class="pp-descriptors">Restful · Present · Renewed</p>
          <div class="pp-mode-badge">Meditate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pp-card-body">
          <p class="pp-guide">Embrace a day of intentional worship and restorative rest. Seek the Lord's presence at church as you sing, take communion, and listen to the reading of the word. Then commit to observing the Sabbath by replacing digital habits with life-giving activities such as reading, journaling, spending time in nature, or engaging in meaningful conversations. Practice saying "no" to productivity and "yes" to savoring God's presence and creation.</p>
          <div class="pp-reflect-section">
            <span class="pp-reflect-label">Reflect</span>
            <ul class="pp-reflect-list">
              <li>What song lyric or Scripture verse stood out to me during church or quiet time?</li>
              <li>Which unfinished tasks or distractions is the Holy Spirit inviting me to rest from today?</li>
              <li>What does "restorative rest" look like for my soul, mind, and body right now?</li>
              <li>Where in nature can I savor God's presence and creation today?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div><!-- /.pp-grid -->

    <!-- AI Prompt -->
    <div class="pp-ai-prompt">
      <span class="pp-ai-label">AI Prompt</span>
      <p>Walk me through today's prayer posture ([INSERT DAY / MODE]) one section at a time. Ask me the reflection questions one by one and push back if my answers are surface-level. Help me get specific — names, situations, and honest acknowledgment. Don't move on until we've gone deep. End by helping me turn my answers into a written prayer.</p>
    </div>

  </div><!-- /.takeaways-content -->
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  /* ─── Page wrapper ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pp-page {
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  /* ─── Page header ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pp-subtitle {
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #7a7368;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ─── Card grid ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pp-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  /* ─── Individual card ───────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pp-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    border: 1px solid rgba(199, 187, 170, 0.45);
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: box-shadow 0.25s;
  }

  .pp-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(70, 61, 52, 0.09);
  }

  /* ─── Card header ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pp-card-top {
    background: rgba(70, 61, 52, 0.04);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(199, 187, 170, 0.4);
    padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem 1rem;
  }

  .pp-day {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #3d3830;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .pp-descriptors {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: #9e8c78;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .pp-mode-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #f3efe9;
    background: #8a7e6e;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  /* ─── Card body ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pp-card-body {
    padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem 1rem;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .pp-guide {
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #5e554b;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0.9rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(199, 187, 170, 0.3);
  }

  /* ─── Reflect section ───────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pp-reflect-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .pp-reflect-label {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #b79c5c;
  }

  .pp-reflect-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .pp-reflect-list li {
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: #5e554b;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ─── AI Prompt ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pp-ai-prompt {
    background: rgba(70, 61, 52, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(199, 187, 170, 0.45);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .pp-ai-label {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #f3efe9;
    background: #6a6156;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  .pp-ai-prompt p {
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    color: #5e554b;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ─── Responsive ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .pp-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .pp-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .pp-ai-prompt {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .pp-day {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
